                    &copy; <a class="border-bottom" href="#">LMS Project</a>, All Right Reserved. Designed By <a class="border-bottom" href="">ABC & team</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-end">
                    <div class="footer-menu">
